        "text": "1 Chronicles 26:26",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " they are separated, and placed under the oversight of two Levite families: the treasures of the house of Jahve under the sons of the Gershonite Laadan (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 26:21",
        "children": []
      },
